{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775885309534,"sessionID":"ses_284fd1305fferLawGsstvfmYgv","part":{"id":"prt_d7b0352f4001EpKwQr3823bPqH","messageID":"msg_d7b033ece001nNDNwvIWfUgwvI","sessionID":"ses_284fd1305fferLawGsstvfmYgv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b32ed24facee480f8198958265209ac0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-031 — RBAC 配置 |\n8: | Module | `manifests` |\n9: | Language | YAML |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: [TO BE FILLED: Define scope for RBAC 配置]\n16: \n17: ## Out of Scope\n18: \n19: [TO BE FILLED: Define out of scope items]\n20: \n21: ## Dependencies\n22: \n23: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n24: |------------|---------|---------|\n25: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n26: \n27: ## Deliverables\n28: \n29: | File | Description |\n30: |------|-------------|\n31: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n32: \n33: ## Acceptance Criteria\n34: \n35: - [ ] [TO BE FILLED]\n36: \n37: ## References\n38: \n39: - [TO BE FILLED: Add relevant references]\n\n(End of file - total 39 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-031 — RBAC 配置 |\n| Module | `manifests` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define scope for RBAC 配置]\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define out of scope items]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md","